Source: neovim
Section: editors
Maintainer: Local Builder <builder@localhost>
Build-Depends: debhelper-compat (= 13), curl
Homepage: https://github.com/neovim/neovim

Package: neovim
Architecture: amd64
Description: Vim-fork focused on extensibility and usability.
 Neovim is a refactor, and sometimes redactor, in the tradition of Vim.
 It is not a rewrite but a continuation and extension of Vim. It features
 modern defaults, a built-in LSP client, and Lua scripting support.
